      </ol>
    </nav>

    <!-- Article Header -->
    <header class="pt-16 pb-8 px-4 bg-gradient-to-b from-stone-50 to-white">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] mb-3">Buyer Guide</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 leading-tight mb-3">
          Puppy Health Guarantee: What It Actually Covers (and What It Doesn't)
        </h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">Last Reviewed: {lastReviewedMonthYear}</p>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          A teardown of the four most common health-guarantee clause types, what each one really commits the breeder to, and the questions to ask before you sign.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 border-t border-stone-200 pt-6">
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">BreederHQ Editorial</p>
            <p>Last Reviewed {lastReviewedMonthYear}</p>
          </div>
          <span class="text-gray-300">·</span>
          <p>May 13, 2026</p>
          <span class="text-gray-300">·</span>
